        "sanitize": false,
        "show": null,
        "text": "<p><span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_SimpleMainContent_MainContent_ucDynamicFormWizard_ctl142\">Fill out this section to identify another person authorized to represent the applicant about the project.</span><br /><span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_SimpleMainContent_MainContent_ucDynamicFormWizard_ctl144\"></span><br /><span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_SimpleMainContent_MainContent_ucDynamicFormWizard_ctl146\">If you are an authorized agent applying for an applicant, your contact information must be included in this section of the application. DFW will not accept applications in which a registered user submits an application but their contact information does not appear in the applicant and/or authorized agent section. If you are an authorized agent, you will be required to upload an attachment to document the applicant&rsquo;s consent; attachment must have applicant&rsquo;s signatures. To download a copy of the document <a href=\"https://www.govonlinesaas.com/WA/WDFW/Public/Public/Doc/Agent_Authorization_Letter.doc\" title=\"Authorization of Agent\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">click here.</a></span></p>",
